`q-r`
`Polymer wrapper for a qr code.`

Attributes:

  * `data` {`string`} - Data to code via QR code

  * `title` {`string`} - Alternate title for the data

  * `modulesize` {`number`} - module size of the square

  * `margin` {`number`} - Margin on the square

  * `format` {`string`} - format to output
